{
    "T15n1144u_001:0": " |Nītiśāstram ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:1": " ||sarvajñāya namaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:2": " arthaśāstraviśeṣādyaḥ śāstreṣu hitakārakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:3": " unmeṣāya nṛṇāṃ buddhe rmasūrākṣeṇa bhāṣitaḥ ||1 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:4": " śreyase ceha saṃsāre jñānopasthāpanāya vai |",
    "T15n1144u_001:5": " vākyaiśca jñānaśikṣāyai yathāvadarthasiddhaye |",
    "T15n1144u_001:6": " buddherutpādanārtha ca naya eṣaḥ prakathyate ||2 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:7": " kauśalaṃ suprayuñjīta vastujātaṃ parāmṛśan |",
    "T15n1144u_001:8": " saṃrakṣeddharmacaryāṃ hi pratyakṣe'pi pare'pi vā ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:9": " krodhaṃ tyajan viśeṣeṇa paṇḍitāṃśca samāśrayet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:10": " vadannityaṃ ṛtaṃ vākyaṃ vadennāhitavācakam ||3 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:11": " brāhmaṇaṃ pūjayedūbhaktyā nāvamanyeta gāstathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:12": " varjayettādṛśīṃ caryāṃ yasmādvā rājato bhayam ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:13": " naiva kadāpyavajñeyāḥ śatravo nāma ye janāḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:14": " vikatthanāṃ parityajya na bhajennindyavastukam ||4 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:15": " bhojyaṃ hitakaraṃ grāhyaṃ nāvamanyeta bāndhavam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:16": " naiva skandejjvaladvahnimāhavaṃ na vilokayet ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:17": " śrotavyāni ca kāvyāni na kuryātprāṇanāśanam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:18": " na skandet vivare kūpe nākṛtyaṃ ca samācaret ||5 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:19": " vidyāṃ labdhvā samāsena na krīḍedahinā saha |",
    "T15n1144u_001:20": " dānaṃ yacchet yathāśakti hīnānnaiva ca kāṅkṣayet",
    "T15n1144u_001:21": " paranindā na kartavyā na tathātmastutiḥ svayam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:22": " niśā'ṭanaṃ na kartavyam jñātavyaṃ tat sadaiva hi ||6 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:23": " na gacchedupa ṣaṇḍaṃ vā chinnabandhanaśṛṅgiṇam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:24": " bandhuhīno'nupānatko na gacchecca pathi kkacit |",
    "T15n1144u_001:25": " dūrādeva varjanīyau duṣṭabuddhiśca nindakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:26": " duṣṭāṃ bhāryāṃ parityajya viśvastāṃ tāṃ samāśrayet ||7 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:27": " yo hi na jñāyate samyaṅ na bhavettena saṃgatiḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:28": " na kāmyeta kadācidvā bhūpateḥ paricārikā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:29": " hitaṃ vākyaṃ sadā śṛṇvanna krudhyet yatra tatra vā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:30": " dhenuṃ sadyaḥprasūtāṃ ca varjayeddūrameva tām ||8 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:31": " na kadā viśvasennāryāṃ na viśeddustarāṃ nadīm |",
    "T15n1144u_001:32": " nāroheduccavṛkṣeṣu pivanmadyaṃ kadāpi vā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:33": " neṣṭalābhāya saṃtyājyaṃ svadharmo svadhanaṃ tathā | ||9 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:34": " tacca sthānaṃ sadā tyājyaṃ rakṣāhīnaṃ tu yadbhavet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:35": " sarveṣāṃ gūḍhavākyāni sarvaśo na prakāśayet ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:36": " bhūtirna sañcitā yena sadodyukto jano hi saḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:37": " ṛtaṃ vākyaṃ vadennityaṃ na bhāṣeta nirarthakam ||10 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:38": " svāgatañca vadennityamāgataṃ purato janam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:39": " naradevadvijāḥ pūjyāḥ puṇyaṃ viṣayamāśrayet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:40": " bhajennityaṃ parisnātaṃ śubhravāsaḥsamanvitam ||11 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:41": " tyajetsaṃgaṃ bahustrīṇāṃ yathā''caranti paṇḍitāḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:42": " dīrghamāyustathā prājño nairujyamadhigacchati ||12 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:43": " iti prathamo'dhyāyaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:44": " pararandhraṃ svarandhraṃ vā gopāyedvā sutaṃ priyām |",
    "T15n1144u_001:45": " pṛthivīva samadraṣṭā mānavaḥ sukhamaśnute ||1 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:46": " marmavākyaṃ na vaktavyaṃ gūḍhaṃ naiva prakāśayet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:47": " bhāṣitaṃ marmavākyaṃ ca jñāyatāṃ śastradhṛgyathā ||2 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:48": " asandigdhamanā bhūtvā vadedikṣuraso yathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:49": " vikṣubdho vacasā yo hi vākyaśalyena hanyate ||3 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:50": " ripavaḥ priyavaktāro na mānyante sadā budhaiḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:51": " viṣabhāṇḍasamāste hi carame kṣayakārakāḥ ||4 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:52": " na manyeta nadīvegaṃ praśastatāṃ tu lakṣayet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:53": " kālo dhāvati tadbaddhi ātmano'rthān vicintayet ||5 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:54": " tāvad bhayasya bhetavyaṃ yāvadbhayamanāgatam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:55": " āgataṃ tu bhayaṃ vīkṣya prahartavyamabhītavat ||6 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:56": " arthāt palāyate jñānaṃ mārjārānmūṣiko yathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:57": " bakavat jñāyatāmarthaḥ siṃhavacca jayedripum ||7 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:58": " siṃhādekaṃ bakādekaṃ ṣaṭ śunastrīṇi gardabhāt |",
    "T15n1144u_001:59": " vāyasāt pañca śikṣecca catvāri kukkuṭādapi ||8 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:60": " prabhūtamalpakāryaṃ vā yo naraḥ kurtumicchati |",
    "T15n1144u_001:61": " sarvārambheṇa tatkuryātsiṃhādekaṃ prakīrtitam ||9 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:62": " sarvendriyāṇi saṃyamya bakavat paṇḍito janaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:63": " kāladeśopapannāni kāryāṇi tu parīkṣayet ||10 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:64": " yuddhaṃ ca prātarutthānaṃ bhojanaṃ saha bandhubhiḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:65": " striyamāpadgatāṃ rakṣeccatuḥ śikṣeta kukkuṭāta ||11 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:66": " gūḍhamaithunadhārṣṭya ca kāle cā''layasaṃgraham |",
    "T15n1144u_001:67": " apramāda [maviśvastaṃ] pañca śikṣeta vāyasāt ||12 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:68": " bahvāśī svalpasantuṣṭhaḥ sunidraḥ śīghracetanaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:69": " prabhorbhaktaśca śūraśca jñātavyāḥ ṣaṭ śuno guṇāḥ ||13 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:70": " aviśrāntaṃ vahedbhāraṃ śītoṣṇaṃ ca na vindati |",
    "T15n1144u_001:71": " [santoṣaśca ] tathā nityaṃ trīṇi śikṣeta gardabhāt ||14 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:72": " viṃśatyete guṇā jñeyā yastu kuryād vicakṣaṇaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:73": " sa jeṣyati ripūn sarvānajeyaśca bhaviṣyati ||15 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:74": " || iti dvitīyo'dhyāyaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:75": " skandhenāpi vahecchatruṃ yāvanna kālasya paryayaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:76": " tathaiva kālasamprāpte bhindyāt ghaṭamivāśmabhiḥ ||1 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:77": " na gacchedīdṛśaṃ śatruṃ roti hīno bhṛśaṃ yathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:78": " tena maitrī na kartavyā ya ādau pratighātakaḥ ||2 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:79": " ṛṇaśeṣaścāgniśeṣaḥ śatruśeṣastathaiva ca |",
    "T15n1144u_001:80": " punaḥ punaḥ pravardhante tasmāccheṣaṃ na rakṣayet ||3 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:81": " kṛte pratikṛtiṃ kuryāddhiṃsane pratihiṃsanam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:82": " tatra doṣaṃ na paśyāmi śaṭhe śāṭhyaṃ samācaret ||4 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:83": " āpadarthe ghanaṃ rakṣet dārān rakṣed ghanairapi |",
    "T15n1144u_001:84": " ātmānaṃ satataṃ rakṣet dārairapi ghanairapi ||5 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:85": " parokṣe kāryahantāraṃ pratyakṣe priyavādinam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:86": " varjayettādṛśaṃ mitraṃ viṣakumbhaṃ payomukham ||6 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:87": " lubdhamartha pradānena ślāghyamañjalikarmaṇā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:88": " mūrkhaṃ chandānuvṛttyā ca yāthātathyena paṇḍitam ||7 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:89": " śatruṃ sāñjaliviśvāsaiḥ saṃpūjya natamaulibhiḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:90": " kāmādaśru vimuñcanti īpsitāḥ dhanakāmukāḥ ||8 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:91": " balīyasi praṇamatāṃ jayecca durbalaṃ ripum |",
    "T15n1144u_001:92": " sandhimicchet samenāpi vigrahaṃ na samācaret ||9 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:93": " na tat kuryādyathodvegaṃ nācareddāruṇaṃ tathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:94": " nātkṣipedyaḥ śiraḥpātaḥ khaṇḍakarma rabhet na ||10 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:95": " na vastavyamareḥ sthāne rabheta kalahaṃ na vā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:96": " na yeṣāṃ vidyate bhedaḥ kutastān bhedayiṣyasi |",
    "T15n1144u_001:97": " nonmūlayettarīrmūlaṃ yanmūlaṃ ca dṛḍhaṃ bhavet ||11 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:98": " na sā sabhā yatra na santi vṛddhā",
    "T15n1144u_001:99": " vṛddhā na te ye na vadanti dharmam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:100": " dharmaḥ sa no yatra na ramyamasti",
    "T15n1144u_001:101": " satyaṃ na tad yacchaladoṣayuktam ||12 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:102": " kliśnāti kaṇṭakaṃ biddhaṃ naṣṭo dharmastathaiva ca |",
    "T15n1144u_001:103": " śatrūṇāṃ ca viruddhānāṃ mūlanāśāt sukhī bhava ||13 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:104": " nātyantaṃ saralairbhāvyaṃ gatvā paśya vanasthalīm |",
    "T15n1144u_001:105": " chidyante saralāstatra kubjāstiṣṭhanti pādapāḥ ||14 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:106": " yadyadā cintitaṃ kiñcittadaiva hitacintitam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:107": " paṇḍitaśca tathākārī tūrṇamātmavaśaṃ nayet ||15 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:108": " yadapasarati meṣaḥ kāraṇaṃ tat prahartuṃ",
    "T15n1144u_001:109": " mṛgapatiratikopāt saṃkucatyutpatiṣṇuḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:110": " hṛdayanihitavairā gūḍhamantropacārāḥ",
    "T15n1144u_001:111": " kimiva hi gaṇayanto buddhimantaḥ kṣamante ||16 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:112": " kutaḥ kokilaḥ sauvarṇyaṃ balmīkaṃ raupyamāskhikam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:113": " ko naṣṭo nāgate kāle bhujaṃgasya padaṃ nu kim ||17 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:114": " padasthaṃ nāvamanyeta matimantaṃ ya āśrayet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:115": " namitaṃ na phaṭāsthānaṃ yasya na kṣayito viṣaḥ ||18 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:116": " na viśvaset pūrvaparājitasya",
    "T15n1144u_001:117": " śatrośca mitratvamupāgatasya |",
    "T15n1144u_001:118": " mṛgo yathā nīravapādaśabdai",
    "T15n1144u_001:119": " rnihanyate vyādhaviṣāktavāṇaiḥ ||19 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:120": " || atha tṛtīyo'dhyāyaḥ samāptaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:121": " ayaṃ svārthaḥ parārtho'yamityevaṃ vā na kalpayet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:122": " vibudhā naiva manyante svaṃ paraṃ vā pṛthak pṛthak",
    "T15n1144u_001:123": " niyuñjīta parasyārthe protsaheta svakarmaṇi ||1 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:124": " añjanasya kṣayaṃ dṛṣṭā valmīkasya ca sañcayam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:125": " budhastathaiva yuñjīta stokena sañcitaṃ yathā ||2 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:126": " dhūrto mohayate sarvān mūḍho muhyati nityaśaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:127": " aviśvasteṣu viśvāsāt svaguptimanucintayet ||3 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:128": " valmīkasya vināśo vai kīṭaniṣṭhīvanādbhavet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:129": " abandhyaṃ divasaṃ kuryād dānādhyayanakarmabhiḥ ||4 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:130": " sajjano'pi sadā mānyo nāśrayedvā khalaṃ tathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:131": " ripuṃ jayecca śauryeṇa śaṭhe naiva ca viśvaset ||5 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:132": " bahiṣkāryā sadā veśyā kṣantavyo hi gurustathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:133": " viśvaṃ yena parijñeyaṃ jagatyāṃ nāśakaṃ tathā ||6 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:134": " sārthakaṃ karma yasya syāt sajjate tara vai janaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:135": " ramyaṃ yatra vacaḥ samyak guṇānākhyāti nityaśaḥ ||7 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:136": " na viśvasedaviśvaste viśvaste nātiviśvaset |",
    "T15n1144u_001:137": " viśvāsādbhayamutpannaṃ sarvaṃ mūlādvinaśyati ||8 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:138": " na grāhyaṃ bhautikaṃ sarvaṃ śatruśaktau na viśvaset |",
    "T15n1144u_001:139": " gūhennityaṃ svabhāvaṃ ca parabhāvaṃ ca lakṣayet ||9 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:140": " paradārā viṣāstulyāḥ evaṃ ca paracārikāḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:141": " mṛtyudvārāṇi vindante viśvāsādubhayostayoḥ ||10 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:142": " āyuryauvanabhogeṣu ripāvūrddhe bhujaṃgame |",
    "T15n1144u_001:143": " viśvāso naiva [vijñānāṃ ] strīṣu rājakuleṣu ca ||11 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:144": " jñānārthamāśrayennityaṃ śraddhavā paṇḍitaṃ janam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:145": " evaṃ jñānārthinā sarvaṃ jñātavyamityaśeṣataḥ ||12 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:146": " viśvāso naiva pāpeṣu paṇḍitairnātmapūjanam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:147": " yatasteṣu na viśvāso jīvikā naśyate nṛṇām ||13 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:148": " antakaḥ parano mṛtyuḥ pātālaṃ vaḍavāmukham |",
    "T15n1144u_001:149": " kṣuradhārā viṣaṃ sarpo vahnivityekataḥ striyaḥ ||14 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:150": " śatrupakṣaḥ parityājya ścātmānande samāśritaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:151": " sarvato buddhimāneṣa ciraṃ nandati bhūyasā ||15 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:152": " cakṣurnimeṣamātraṃ vā na parokṣe ripuḥ kṛtaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:153": " nāśayet kālakhaḍgena nindāyāṃ vadhirastathā ||16 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:154": " yatrodakaṃ tatra vasanti haṃsāstathaiva śuṣkaṃ parivarjayanti |",
    "T15n1144u_001:155": " na haṃsatulyena nareṇa bhāvyaṃ punastyajanti punarāśrayanti ||17 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:156": " rājñaḥ saṅgaṃ na yāceta gaṇikāyāstathaiva hi |",
    "T15n1144u_001:157": " bhiṣajo vā kuṭumbānāṃ bhṛtyānāṃ naiva naiva ca ||18 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:158": " yasyaiva kāraṇājjātaṃ śoko duḥkhaṃ tathā kṣatiḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:159": " śarīre nāśamūlaṃ vai kiñcinmātraṃ budhastyajet ||19 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:160": " yathā caturbhiḥ kanakaṃ parīkṣyate",
    "T15n1144u_001:161": " nirgharṣaṇacchedanatāpatāḍanaiḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:162": " tathā caturbhiḥ puruṣaḥ parīkṣyate",
    "T15n1144u_001:163": " tyāgena śīlena kulena vidyayā ||20 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:164": " jānīyāt yogyakālaṃ vai rakṣed guptiṃ svakaṃ param |",
    "T15n1144u_001:165": " lokacittavinodāya vākyeṣu viśvasetsadā ||21 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:166": " |'tha caturtho'dhyāyaḥ samāptaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:167": " amātyo jñānasampannaḥ sarvaśāstraviśāradaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:168": " koṣavān balavāṃścaiva yo na hanyāt sa hanyate ||1 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:169": " viśvastā hi mariṣyanti yathā vaṃśaḥ phalena hi |",
    "T15n1144u_001:170": " viśvāsānnāśamāyāti yathāraṇye sthito mṛgaḥ ||2 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:171": " ānandayati sattvāni yo hi maṅgalamañjuvāk |",
    "T15n1144u_001:172": " nindāmeṣyati loke saḥ paravākyanigūhakaḥ ||3 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:173": " cetasā yo mahāpāpaḥ pāpakṛt doṣayuktakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:174": " eṣa panthāḥ khalācāro mānabhaṅgena nāśitaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:175": " śaṭhaśca nagaradhvaṃsī lokeṣu durjano ripuḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:176": " kujanānāṃ nidhiḥ so'pi kūpo vā malino yathā ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:177": " mukhaṃ miṣṭaṃ ca mādhvīkam vākyaṃ candanaśītalam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:178": " cittaṃ karāta sadṛśamevaṃ sa dhūrtapūruṣaḥ ||5 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:179": " priyabhāṣī svayaṃ dhūrto doṣānukāyamañju vāk |",
    "T15n1144u_001:180": " prītirna dhriyate citte kapaṭī sa yamāntakaḥ ||6 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:181": " atinīcāni vākyāni dṛṣṭimātrātinindakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:182": " kṣudrasaṃvādabhāṣī yo hyevaṃ duṣṭaḥ śaṭho janaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:183": " purā yena kṛto nāśo'dhunā yena ca nāśitaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:184": " viśvāso'tra na kartavyaḥ koṭarasthita-sarpavat ||8 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:185": " nakhināṃ ca nadīnāṃ ca śṛṃgiṇāṃ śastrapāṇinām |",
    "T15n1144u_001:186": " viśvāso naiva kartavyaḥ strīṣu rājakuleṣu ca ||9 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:187": " agnirāpaḥ striyo mūrkho sarpo rājakulaṃ tathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:188": " bhūyānnityaṃ satarko'taḥ sadyaḥprāṇaharāṇi ṣaṭ ||10 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:189": " śatrave riṃkthadāyī yo nāśritavyaḥ kadācana |",
    "T15n1144u_001:190": " nāśayatyapi sa prāṇān yathā māyi-dvicāriṇī ||11 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:191": " varjayettādṛśaṃ bandhumādāvaniṣṭakāriṇam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:192": " mitravāñchāṃ na gṛhṇāti hetuḥ kalahakāriṇām ||12 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:193": " bandhuṃ na yo vijānāti mitraṃ parijanāṃstathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:194": " pravīṇasevakān bhṛtyāṃścaivaṃ sa itaro janaḥ ||13 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:195": " na sambhāṣeta cauraṃ vā bandhuṃ vā'riṣṭavāhinam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:196": " dvijaṃ pāpakṛtaṃ naiva striyaṃ ca vyabhicāriṇīm ||14 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:197": " na dūṣayet paraṃ tatra nātmanā yat parīkṣitam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:198": " na kuryādīdṛśaṃ karma narake patanaṃ yataḥ ||15 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:199": " ātmaiva hyātmano mitramātmaiva ripurātmanaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:200": " svargo vā narakastatra sarvamātmavaśāspadam ||16 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:201": " iti pañcamo'dhyāyaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:202": " yathā hi bhāsate sūryo dīptyā sarvaṃ prakāśate |",
    "T15n1144u_001:203": " tathaiva rājate mantrī sarvvatra samadarśakaḥ ||1 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:204": " khale sakhyaṃ prāṅmadhuraṃ vadho'ntarāle nidāghadinamante |",
    "T15n1144u_001:205": " ekādimadhyapariṇatiramaṇīyā sādhujanamaitrī ||2 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:206": " mahātmanā samaṃ prītirādau śīrṇatamā matā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:207": " samyagvibardhate madhye hyante tu pariramyate ||3 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:208": " sādhoḥ prītirnadīvaddhi śīrṇā''dau mahatī param |",
    "T15n1144u_001:209": " bardhate ca krameṇāsau naivā''vṛttiśca karhicit ||4 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:210": " gāvo gandhena paśyanti vedaiścaiva dvijātayaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:211": " karṇaiḥ paśyanti rājāno bheṣajairbhiṣajastathā ||5 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:212": " ghātakāmanayā śatrustoṣṭavyo miṣṭabhāṣaṇaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:213": " nityaṃ cittavimohena gītamugdho mṛgo yathā ||6 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:214": " yasyārthāstasya mitrāṇi yasyārthāstasya bāndhavāḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:215": " yasyārthāḥ sa pumālloke yasyārthāḥ sa hi paṇḍitaḥ ||7 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:216": " tyajanti mitrāṇi dhanairvihīnaṃ puttāṃśca dārāṃśca suhṛjjanāṃśca |",
    "T15n1144u_001:217": " tamarthavantaṃ punarāśrayante'pyartho hi loke puruṣasya bandhuḥ ||8 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:218": " adṛṣṭapūrvo bahavaḥ sahāyāḥ sarve padasthasya bhavanti vaśyāḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:219": " arthairvihīnasya padacyūtasya bhaveddhi kāle svajano'pi śatruḥ ||9 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:220": " mantraṃ gūheta yatnena samyagbalena sādhayet |",
    "T15n1144u_001:221": " ripornaiva ca bhetavyaṃ ripurbheṣyatyasaṃśayam ||10 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:222": " mūlanāśaṃ vipakśāṇāmādau karoti paṇḍitaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:223": " tataḥ svapakṣayogena hanyatāṃ pūrvapīḍakaḥ ||11 |",
    "T15n1144u_001:224": " sakṛdduṣṭantu yo mitraṃ punaḥ sandhātumicchati |",
    "T15n1144u_001:225": " sa mṛtyumupagṛhṇāti garbhamaśvatarī yathā ||12 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:226": " vairiṇā saha viśvāsaṃ yo naraḥ kartumicchati |",
    "T15n1144u_001:227": " sa vṛkṣāgreṣu suptaḥ san patitvā pratihanyate ||13 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:228": " pitā''cāryaḥ suhṛnmātā bhāryā putraḥ purohitaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:229": " rājño'ntarghātako yo hi sa hantavyo na saṃśayaḥ ||14 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:230": " mṛdunaiva mṛduṃ hanti mṛdunā hanti dāruṇam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:231": " nāvaśyaṃ mṛdunā kiñcittasmāttīkṣṇataro mṛduḥ ||15 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:232": " tulyārthaṃ tulyasāmarthyaṃ mantrajñaṃ vyavasāyinam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:233": " argharājyaharaṃ bhṛtyaṃ yo na hanyāt sa hanyate ||16 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:234": " gāmbhīryayuktā mṛdumandavākyā",
    "T15n1144u_001:235": " jitendriyāḥ satyaparāḥ suyojyāḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:236": " bhāvyarthatajjñā viditārthatattvāḥ",
    "T15n1144u_001:237": " prāyeṇa bhṛtyāḥ kṛtino bhavanti ||17 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:238": " nirālasyāḥ susaṃhṛṣṭāḥ susvapnāḥ pratibodhakāḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:239": " sukhaduḥkhasamā dhīrā bhṛtyā lokeṣu durlabhāḥ ||18 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:240": " sarale saralo bhūtvā kuṭile kuṭilastathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:241": " sukhini ca sukhī bhūtvā vyathite vyathitastathā ||19 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:242": " yo yasminnandate bhāve nareṇa haśyate'valā",
    "T15n1144u_001:243": " satāṃ veśmapraveśadvāḥ notsṛjyate kadāpi vā ||20 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:244": " durjanaiḥ saha vāsena sujano durjanāyate |",
    "T15n1144u_001:245": " paṃkilaṃ paṃkayogena nirmalaṃ hi jalaṃ yathā ||21 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:246": " mukhe vahati mādhuryaṃ hṛdaye kṣārasannibham |",
    "T15n1144u_001:247": " komalamaśmacūrṇaṃ hi kaṭhinābhyantaraṃ sadā ||22 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:248": " kadāpi nāśrayetprājño'karuṇaṃ miṣṭabhāṣiṇam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:249": " pracchannamasahiṣṇuṃ vā guḍamiśraṃ viṣaṃ yathā ||23 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:250": " nātidhūrteṣu viśvāso naiva sandhirna cā''śrayaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:251": " amlena bardhate nityaṃ yathā vyādhirvisūcikā ||24 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:252": " mahātarurvā bhavati samūlo vā vinaśyati |",
    "T15n1144u_001:253": " nāntarapratyayāneti nyagrodhakaṇikāṃkuraḥ ||24 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:254": " putrāḥ pautrā vinaśyanti vinaṣṭe narapālake |",
    "T15n1144u_001:255": " āśritāḥ sacivā bhṛtyā nyagrodhasyāṃ'kure yathā ||25 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:256": " ||iti ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:257": " pārthivasyeva vakṣyāmi bhṛtyānāṃ caiva lakṣaṇam |",
    "T15n1144u_001:258": " sabāndhavo mahīpālaḥ samyag bhṛtyān parīkṣayet ||1 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:259": " pūjyate mānavairdevairindrādidaivataṃ yathā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:260": " tathaiva pūjyate rājā prajābhirmantribhiḥ saha ||2 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:261": " sthiragambhīrabuddhiśca tejasvī dharmaśāstravit |",
    "T15n1144u_001:262": " satyavādī vinītaśca rājño janahite matiḥ ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:263": " kuśaladhīḥ kulīnaśca gurau bhaktiparāyaṇaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:264": " prajānāṃ vatsalaścaiva yuvarājaḥ sa ucyate ||3 |4 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:265": " kalyāṇahitavān bhūpo gurūṇāṃ doṣaguptakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:266": " samamatiḥ sukhe duḥkhe samare cāpalāyitaḥ",
    "T15n1144u_001:267": " kulaśīleṣu sampanno nītidharmeṣu paṇḍitaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:268": " tathaiva pūjyate rājā caturasraḥ prakīrtitaḥ ||6 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:269": " vākpaṭu rbuddhisampanno nītiśāstreṣu paṇḍitaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:270": " miṣṭālāpī sadācāro rājamantrī tathaiva hi ||7 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:271": " medhāvī vākpaṭuḥ prājñaḥ paracittopalakṣakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:272": " dhīro yathoktavādī ca eṣa dūto vidhīyate ||8 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:273": " vedavedāṅgatattvajño japahomaparāyaṇaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:274": " āśīrvādaparo nityameṣa [prājñaḥ] purohitaḥ ||9 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:275": " sakṛduktagṛhītārtho laghuhasto jitākṣaraḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:276": " śabdaśāstraparijñātā eṣa lekhaka iṣyate ||10 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:277": " varṇāñchabdāṃśca yo vetti śabdatattvavicakṣaṇaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:278": " vidheyaḥ pāṭhako hyeva gandharvaḥ svaravidyathā ||11 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:279": " śubhāśubhaphalābhijño dhīraḥ prājño jitandriyaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:280": " daṇḍādhikārikaḥ śuddho nṛpasya deharakṣakaḥ ||12 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:281": " āyurvedakṛtābhyāsaḥ sarveṣāṃ priyadarśanaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:282": " [śīlavidhiṣu sampanno ] vaidyo eṣa vidhīyate ||13 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:283": " balavānmadhuvaktaścā 'parāñjānāti yo laghu |",
    "T15n1144u_001:284": " parāśayasadābhijño vidheyaḥ pālakaḥ sadā ||14 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:285": " śastreṣu kuśalī dakṣo vāhaneṣu suśikṣakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:286": " dhairya vīryaguṇopetaḥ senādhyakṣo vidhīyate ||15 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:287": " pitṛpaitāmaho dakṣaḥ śāstrajño miṣṭapācakaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:288": " śaucaprītisamāyuktaḥ sūpakāraḥ sa ucyate ||16 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:289": " śānto vinītaḥ kuśalaḥ satkulīnaḥ śubhānvitaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:290": " śāstrārthatattvago'mātyo bhaved bhūmibhujāmiha ||17 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:291": " dhīro'pi vijayī rājā śvetacchatrapatākayā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:292": " śobhate samare nityaṃ tasya kīrtirbhaved dhruvā ||18 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:293": " śuṣkāsthikhaṇḍaṃ prati lobhinā śunā |",
    "T15n1144u_001:294": " bhūyo'pi daṃṣṭrābhiridaṃ hi daśyate |",
    "T15n1144u_001:295": " lelihyate srāvi sukhena śoṇitaṃ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:296": " tathaiva tṛṣṇārtajanaḥ sukhe rataḥ ||19 ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:297": " iti saptamo'dhyāyaḥ |",
    "T15n1144u_001:298": " atha masūrākṣapraṇītanītiśāstraṃ samāptam ||",
    "T15n1144u_001:299": " bhāratīyapaṇḍitadharmaśrīvajrena bhauṭṭabhikṣuśākyamatyā ca",
    "T15n1144u_001:300": " saṃskṛtabhāṣāyā bhoṭabhāṣāyāmanūditamidamiti |"
}